---
title: Plant-Based Chick'n Tenders & Spiced Wedges with Burger Sauce & Avocado Salad
description: A plant-based version of chicken tenders, yes it can be done. A side of golden wedges to dip in a burger sauce (it’s great for the
chicken tenders too!) will make your mouth water in no time.
